name: The North Sector Warden
description:
The Wardens is a near extinct group of brigands trying to reclaim their forest from demonic occupiers.

They used to be magi, shamans and druids, but as their methods turned more and more violent, they lost the knowledge of their ancestors.

The North Sector Warden is responsible for carrying out insurgencies in the north.
